fehd.ADR_TC: 九龍尖沙咀柯士甸道西3號香港西九龍站B2層抵港大堂 WEK B2-10號舖主要部份

reviews.text: Many restaurants combined together. One ordering counter and one pick up counter. The flavours were decent but the baked porkchop with rice was lacking a bit of sauce. The drink was also fine. The overall is a bit pricy though, around 50-60$ for a meal.

來到西九龍高鐵站坐車前想食點東西~
去了堂前食坊這個Food Court看看
發現地方也挻大的 而且環境也不錯耶

在大堂的正中間位置 會有數個卡位可以坐
而用來分開的牆壁就竟然是湯匙陣🤭
挻有趣及新鮮的感覺 挻現代風格的環境

·海南雞飯套餐 HKD$88
·吉列豬扒飯套餐 HKD$82
·凍咖啡 HKD$3(跟餐價) 
·椰子汁 HKD$5

食物的份量也不少的🤭 味道不過不失😋
雞肉和豬扒的肉質也不會韌🤤🤤
最怕在街會食到又"鞋"又韌的肉質
以高鐵站來說算是便宜吧 樓上的店鋪貴很多

看到其他店鋪的價錢還要貴一些🙄🙄
所以去這些地方我也會選擇Food Court的

高鐵西九龍總站已經開通了一段日子，今天趁著空檔便來看看。
可能都是開通初期，所以不是很多巴士可以直達這裡。
逛了一會，有點肚餓，便來到B2的美食廣場。
這間堂前食坊，有燒味、馬來食品、米缐、焗飯和三文治。
海龍王麻辣米線套餐$71，蘿蔔、龍蝦丸、魚片和蝦。麻辣不會太辣，其中以蘿蔔最為入味。
新加坡鮮蝦喇沙套餐$71，有蝦、豆卜、魚角、魚蛋、蛋。湯頭的椰香味道十足，配合米粉和配料，味道正宗。
跟餐另加$3凍咖啡，份量不算大，奶味比咖啡濃。
又貴不好吃，可能是租金太高。快要倒閉了。
貴而難吃

result.adr_address: Austin Rd W, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: Austin Rd W, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Hong Kong West Kowloon Station

reviews.text: Huge, spacious and very open station with a central atrium and big windows all around. Has great views of Hong Kong along with his food and drink options. From a transport perspective, it has good connections to the MTR network and taxi & bus stops nearby so it's easy to connect into the broader Hong Kong. It's a nice experience to travel through here!

The pass through if customs is quick with usually less than 10 minutes unless you met several travel tours passing through at the same time. The location can be easily accessed from 2 MTR stations (Kowloon and Austin). It is air conditioned, so it is very comfortable. I like the Milk Tea shop from Taiwan, so I don't need to go Taiwan for its taste.

Very large and spacious, convenient for travellers. There is a beautiful green plaza before entering the Ticketing booths. There are restaurants and souvenir shops before departure. Ticketing can be more efficient if possible

Such a wonderful work of art. Here we can see how architecture plays an important role in the art of a place.
The station is huge and beautiful, I was told that the trains leaving this station travel throughout China but in such an enormous place we barely notice the amount of people that circulates every minute.
Congratulations to all the people involved  in the conception and construction of this beautiful station.
Go there an hour before departure just in case.  Cool and efficient boarder control.  Business class lounge, don't even bother to go up.  No booze no nothing.
